ENB’s Unique Value Proposition
ENB is more than just another Mini App—it’s a community-driven engagement layer. Key features include:

Gamified Interactions: Users earn rewards for participating in casts or completing tasks.
NFT Minting: Based on user scores or activity, ENB can mint ERC-1155 tokens on Base.
Social Discovery: ENB is embedded in Farcaster posts, making it easy to discover and share. [deepwiki.com]

This combination of social virality and onchain utility makes ENB a compelling use case for decentralized apps.
